        <num>CC 3144</num>
        <heading>3144.  Accessory nature of pledge</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 3144.  Accessory nature of pledge
Pledge is accessory to the obligation that it secures and may be enforced by the
pledgee only to the extent that he may enforce the secured obligation.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=110193</p>
